{"tid":2215791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"浴血新城市｜襲兩警認暴動罪 兩男入獄四年 17歲男生囚40個月","createTime":"2020-09-24T08:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:10:34.000Z","uid":202425,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5418917b3bc90760e7fce80557587ba52aff8f","tid":2215791,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"去年7月14日市民發起「光復沙田」示威，惟當晚防暴警突然衝入新城市廣場，繼而爆發激烈警民衝突。其中有兩名警員在兩分鐘內分別遭示威者圍毆並用雨傘等物襲擊。有份施襲的保安員、青年及17歲男學生今在區域法院承認兩項暴動罪。法官胡雅文今判其中兩人入獄四年，17歲男生則囚3年4個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/HXRRYFI2ZFAGHNK2KKSCKXQISY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FHXRRYFI2ZFAGHNK2KKSCKXQISY%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=a5e9c5d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FHXRRYFI2ZFAGHNK2KKSCKXQISY%2F&h=89286da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/HXRRYFI2ZFAGHNK2KKSCKXQISY/</a>"},{"pid":"683a2214ee0ce2081b36c32a7bf3ebbccc2d0d98","tid":2215791,"uid":221987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85696daf62c0f838e66141589714b5e5e915d195","tid":2215791,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"160f04f7df92d33d1093cd6b5d6445918ac44a35","tid":2215791,"uid":226192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49e261e9c7e316cedc957da3f5f150aa226b250","tid":2215791,"ui